    "details": {
      "isComplex": true,
      "level": {
        "value": 10
      },
      "disable": "<p>@Check[type:thievery|dc:31] (expert) to immobilize the lifting floor plates or @Check[type:perception|dc:29] to notice the bypass switch at the entrance of the room</p>",
      "description": "<p>A cruel trap that lifts the floor into slopes to slide intruders in front of deadly iron maidens that stun and stab with deadly spikes.</p><hr /><h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p>A two-stage horror, springing 3 rounds after a creature crosses the lane: the floor tilts 45° (@Check[type:reflex|dc:12] or slide into the kill-lane and fall @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.j91X7x0XSomq8d60]{Prone}), the western maidens wail, the eastern fire spikes.</p>",
      "reset": "<p>The trap deactivates and resets after it has repeated its routine for 4 rounds. The trap takes 1 minute after this to fully reset, filling the room with ominous clicking and grinding. The trap also deactivates and starts to reset once the bypass switch is flipped.</p>",
      "routine": "<p>On the trap's turn each round, the iron maidens along the walls open to reveal an interior lined with spikes. The spikes extend on poles, making a spike skewer Strike against any creature standing in an adjacent square. The spikes then retract into their respective iron maidens.</p>"
    },
